      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, showing it has been well-loved and consistently maintained over the years. It drives smoothly and looks great, making it the perfect choice for someone who values reliability and a well-kept appearance. Don't miss out on this dependable and stylish ride!",
