      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a parts donor. The body has significant rust issues, particularly around the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the paint is heavily faded with clear coat failure on the roof and trunk. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent knock, and the transmission shifts harshly between second and third gears. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It will likely need to be towed and requires substantial work to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The engine and transmission are fully functional and operate reliably. The exterior shows minor cosmetic wear, such as small scratches, and the interior is well-maintained with light signs of use.",
      "price": 33000.0,
