    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic maintenance. This unit has been curated to ensure a seamless driving experience, offering a balanced synergy of performance and comfort. With a documented history of attentive care, it stands as a premier selection for the discerning driver seeking quality without compromise. We invite you to experience the caliber of this automotive investment firsthand.",
      "price": 32450.0,
